e slippage.  This condition can vary by terrain type.</comment><data>{"commentRefs":[],"fieldData":{"~commentOffsetX":"16","~commentOffsetY":"16"}}</data><value name="VALUE"><shadow type="math_number" id="$A9C/ikTqshYU-do%nw="><field name="NUM">20</field></shadow></value><next><block type="variables_set" id="DW$%eCw(%,JDYvX+9;i#"><field name="VAR" id="Pn4_q~v_/TkrLShW@pU.">accel_rate</field><comment pinned="false" h="109" w="459">This variable controls the rate of the acceleration ramp-- how long the bot takes to get from zero to max. In initial testing 1 worked well, 2 produced tire slippage.</comment><data>{"commentRefs":[],"fieldData":{"~commentOffsetX":"16","~commentOffsetY":"16"}}</data><value name="VALUE"><shadow type="math_number" id="pH8fAV{zwYAEvJBbP`HP"><field name="NUM">1</field></shadow></value><next><block type="variables_set" id="a+8@7k8eW!7qWgbq+5q?"><field name="VAR" id="`=ApUrD}(0qDd^Yp4(rh">max_normal_speed</field><value name="VALUE"><shadow type="math_number" id="GEjaSzxl[[lJyQnY][P{"><field name="NUM">40</field></shadow></value><next><block type="variables_set" id="yzk)A.Yg/UY0B?=s*S1z"><field name="VAR" id="Bdy2d{-@DtkKH1)=c_,-">max_turbo_speed</field><comment pinned="false" h="119" w="369">This value will determine the maximum speed to which the bot will accelerate before topping out. Valid range is 0 to 100.</comment><data>{"commentRefs":[],"fieldData":{"~commentOffsetX":"16","~commentOffsetY":"16"}}</data><value name="VALUE"><shadow type="math_number" id="MaXKd[M~-+?_N5!%o=R,"><field name="NUM">99</field></shadow></value><next><block type="quest_Note_1_quest_Show_String_For_Note_Big_Func" id="i942cubxby`}Ka.SfPyd"><value name="textStrIn"><shadow type="text" id="VWciCX6;c(?1#_HFWnRl"><field name="TEXT">Below, Setup Code for Student:</field></shadow></value></block></next></block></next></block></next></block></next></block></next></block></next></block></next></block></next></block></next></block></next></block></next></block></statement></blo